The problem involves two agents, which could fall under the Game Theory (cs.GT) sub-category. The paper also discusses necessary and sufficient conditions for implementability, which could relate to the Mathematics (cs.MA) sub-category. The coordination problem involves an external system state, which could be relevant to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. Finally, the paper addresses the problem using joint distribution, which could be related to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
